                "MOMIX"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "NH(4)-Cl was irradiated 5 min with (NH(4))*2-SO(4).",
                "After chemical separation, 3.13 MeV gamma peak from",
                "S-37 was measured with Ge(Li) detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
